title: Is Russia readying to move troops to 2 new Syria bases?
text:
23 Is Russia readying to move troops to 2 new Syria bases? 
CNN: Russia may be preparing to station troops at two new sites in Syria as it continues its rapid military buildup in the conflict-ravaged nation, a research firm says.IHS Jane's said Tuesday that it had spotted two previously unreported sites in satellite imagery of western Syria where steps appear to be being taken to receive Russian forces.
